    cat: "ai",
    title: "The Nex Playground is down to its pre-RAMageddon price during Prime Day",
    summary: "The Nex Playground is the family-centric, Kinect-like game console that made one Verge editor’s kids laugh, cry, and ask for more playtime, even when they were sick. The motion-based game play isn’t perfect, but it has won over plenty of parents — and it’s on sale for $239 at Amazon, down from its current MSRP [&#8230;]",
    body: "You gotta admit, it looks like fun. | Photo: Sean Hollister / The Verge The Nex Playground is the family-centric, Kinect-like game console that made one Verge editor’s kids laugh, cry, and ask for more playtime , even when they were sick. The motion-based game play isn’t perfect, but it has won over plenty of parents — and it’s on sale for $239 at Amazon , down from its current MSRP of $299. That’s a healthy discount, though only slightly better than the Nex’s original $250 price.\n\nNex Playground What if the dream of Microsoft&#8217;s Kinect lived on? It does in the Nex Playground, an all-in-one, motion-controlled console filled with kid-friendly games. Exhaust and entertain your little ones. You&#8217;re welcome. Where to Buy: $299 $239 at Amazon $299 $239 at Walmart $299.99 $239 at Best Buy Like so many other gadgets, the Nex Playground became a victim of RAMageddon when its price went up in April .\n\nIt got a $60 discount shortly after for Amazon’s week of gaming deals — and again with this Prime Day deal — but it’s nothing like the $199 prices we saw before the RAM crisis hit. This is the new normal, I guess. Still, any discount is welcome, especially when you’ll need a subscription if you want to play more than a few starter games. You can get a 3-month Play Pass for $49 to access a much deeper catalog of games, or pay $89 for a 12-month pass.\n\nThe subscription economy and RAMageddon come for us all, but at least a sale can take a little bit of the sting out of it.",
    source: "The Verge",
    url: "https://www.theverge.com/gadgets/950871/nex-playground-prime-day-deal-sale",
    time: "5 ore fa",
    pub_ts: 1782255600,
